title: Warcraft III RoC + TFT v1.26 Complete (+ lots of LAN maps)
description:
I've created a portable version of the latest Warcraft III release from Battle.net. This means that it's pre-installed and is therefore very easy to share amongst friends on LAN parties.

Version number: 1.26 (latest verision pr march 2015)

Inside this torrent is a .RAR-file which can be opened with WinRAR. The RAR-file contains the entire gamefolder, so you only need to exract the RAR-file and start the game in order to play.

- No crack needed
- Works on Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1
- Works on Local Area Network


The game is completely untouched and original. I've only made it portable and also added alot of maps that has been gathered by my friends over a decade. All maps are sorted by game type like Maul, Siege, Tower Defence, Wars, Footmen, Life as a Peasant etc.

If you get any problems, just write in the comments section below and I'll try to help as best as I can
